go_data.justification: SCFSKP2 is mentioned alongside other components of the ubiquitin ligase complex.
SCFSKP2 is identified as a ubiquitylation target of a Cul1-based core ubiquitin ligase complex.
Phosphorylation of Skp2 regulated by CDK2 and Cdc14B protects it from degradation by APC(Cdh1) in G1 phase.
